casebody.data:
Thursday, July 7, 1994

MOTION DOCKET

87-1159. State v. Van Hook.

Hamilton County, No. C-850565. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Hamilton County. Upon consideration of appellee’s request to strike its motion to set execution date,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the request to strike be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective July 5, 1994.
